title: For Sale:  Colt King Cobra Enhance LNIB
postcontent: Colt King Cobra with the Stainless Finish and the 6” barrel. It is the EDT Model which stands for Enhanced Drilled & Tapped. This model came from Colt with the recessed barrel and drilled and tapped. Comes with the Original Factory Labeled Colt Blue Box and Papers. The story is told by and among Colt enthusiast is that Colt ran out of parts to manufacture the King Cobra Models, so to keep production going they robbed the Cylinder Latches from the Anaconda models and recessed the barrel and named it the "Enhanced" Model. This piece is in EXTRAORDINARY LIKE NEW CONDITION with no signs of being consumer used that we can see. Please review the pictures for the extraordinary condition of this beautiful King Cobra. Very hard to improve on the condition of this Colt. The condition status it is Like New Condition with no signs of ever being "used" in any way that we can see. These Colt King Cobra Models are becoming one of the most sought after and collected model of the Colt Snake guns series simply because Colt didn't produce them but for a limited period of time and not to mention that this one is the EDT Mode. A must have for any collector of Colt Snake guns.
